data.text:
Synaptula lamperti is commonly referred to as Dark-Stripes Worm Sea Cucumber, Pygmy Snake Sea Cucumber, Lampert's sea cucumber. Difficulty in the aquarium: There are no reports available yet that this animal has already been kept in captivity successfully. Toxicity: Toxic hazard unknown.
